  <summary date="2021-05-04T15:17:20Z" status="Introduced in House">COVID Economic Injury Disaster Loan Relief Act

This bill extends the deferment of a borrower's payments on an economic injury disaster loan taken in response to COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) from one year to two years from the date on which the loan is made.</summary>
